title: Dilwyn's Cafe
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This cafe is owned by a woman who is vegetarian and vegan aware. Menu has a vegan section which includes a couple main courses (a chili and a Mediterranean chickpea stew/casserole) prepared with dedicated separate equipment. The accompanying "chips" (fries) are also prepared in a separate vegan fryer. Also there is a veggie-nut burger prepared on the regular grill but after it is washed down.
